body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting PowerTech Support. My name is Dylan Nelson. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello Dylan, my name is Kelly Nelson.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great to meet you, Kelly. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling excited because I recently purchased a new car from your dealership.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: That's fantastic to hear! To better assist you, could you please provide me with the Vehicle Identification Number (VIN) of your new car?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the VIN is one zero zero one two three four five six seven eight nine.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Kelly. Can you also confirm the color of your new car for me?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Perfect, thank you for the information, Kelly. Is there anything else I can help with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all. Thank you for your assistance, Dylan.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Kelly. Thank you for contacting PowerTech Support. Have a great day!
